name: Lemon tits
description: ‘Lemon tits’ is about breaking the boundaries that society has put up. What society tried to ban, is now your favorite bra. Breaking down those social constructs and owning them is represented through ‘Lemon tits’, just as we are breaking down these stigmas in real life. ‘Lemon tits’ is the third nft in the second part of the lemon collection. The second part of the lemon collection tells the rest of the story in 6 illustrations. This part is about becoming and sharing the lemon. Digital artwork made in 2021 by Camila Trapasso (camamblo).
